<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Currently the format is inconsistent and carries unnecessary information (in addition to not being documented).</p>

<p>Suggested Improvement:
- remove the called and method from the XML (they're known)
- wrap any type of response in a  root node
- add the status as an attribute to the response
Success:
&lt;response generator="zend" version="1.0" status="success'&gt;
   
</p>

<ul><li>For exceptions adding the type of exception would be helpful
&lt;response generator="zend" version="1.0" status="failed'&gt;
FooBarException</li>
</ul>
